	 exchanges. Mobile barcodes delayed until 4 days prior to event. Venue res
	erves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each 
	person must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is n
	o elevator. Stairs only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & bag searc
	h at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When
	 purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by ema
	il if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you 
	may reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses
